name: AtRightPrice
tag_list: mobiles, cameras, digital-cameras, laptops, computers, televisions, compare, prices-in-india
overview:
AtRightPrice is the place for shoppers to compare product prices

AtRightPrice, the price comparison website has recently launched where shoppers can compare product prices before they buy. It currently provides price comparison for mobiles, cameras from several online stores. Several product categories will be added to the website in the coming months.

The company is also working with local stores to get price data so that the consumer can find out the best price of any product in one place.

AtRightPrice has been started by a team of people from different backgrounds that include IT and retail marketing with one goal in mind which is to create a website that is believed to be the right place to find the right price of any product that a shopper is looking for.
